examples.en: The Flat Earth Society surely doesn't have many adherents.

examples.en: The anti-globalization movement is attracting new adherents to its principles.

examples.en: The bandage is made from a mildly adherent fiber.
examples.ru: Повязка изготовлена из мягко прилегающего волокна.
